.TH "ccio_alloc_range" 9 "ccio_alloc_range" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ccio_alloc_range \- Allocate pages in the ioc's resource map.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ccio_alloc_range
.BI "(struct ioc *ioc "  ","
.BI "struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ioc" 12
The I/O Controller.
.IP "dev" 12
-- undescribed --
.IP "size" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function searches the resource map of the ioc to locate a range
of available pages for the requested size.
